COMPONENT NAME: CKM SQL
AUTHOR: Oracle, Tim Garrod
Description: - Check Knowledge Module for MSSQL Azure PDW - This module controls the validity of the constraints of a Datastore and rejects the invalid records in an error table. It can be used for static controls as well as flow controls.
Restrictions: - Data cleansing can be performed only if an update key is defined on the controlled table.
-Upgrade: the option UPGRADE_ERROR_TABLE is used to upgrade the error table.

When this option is set to YES, the error table will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This means that any rejected records, identified and stored during previous control operations, will be lost.

When this option is set to YES, the SNP_CHECK_TAB check table (which is created in the default Physical Schema of the Physical Server that hosts the controlled table) will be dropped each time a control is performed on the target table. This table contains a collection of all rejected records retrieved from all datastores hosted on the same Physical Server (whatever the Physical Schema may be).
When this option is set to YES, the existing E$ table and check tables will be dropped and recreate.

IF OBJECT_ID('<%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME","W")%>') IS NULL create table <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME","W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , SCHEMA_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , RESOURCE_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, FULL_RES_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "100", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_MESS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> , CHECK_DATE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ORIGIN <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "128", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, CONS_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ERR_COUNT DECIMAL(10) <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> )

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> where CATALOG_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>' and SCHEMA_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>' and ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>'

IF OBJECT_ID('<%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%>') IS NULL create table <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_ERR_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "1", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_ERR_MESS <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CHECK_DATE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_DATE", "", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]\t\t[DEST_WRI_DT] " + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL"), ",\n\t", "", "")%>, ODI_ORIGIN <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "250", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CONS_NAME <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "128", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_CONS_TYPE <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "2", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%>, ODI_SESS_NO <%=odiRef.getDataType("DEST_VARCHAR", "36", "")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DDL_NULL")%> )

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> where (ODI_ERR_TYPE = 'S' and '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' = 'S') or (ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>')

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_SESS_NO, ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getPK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getPK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'PK', <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where <%=odiRef.getColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]	= E.[COL_NAME]", "
		and	", "", "PK")%> group by <%=odiRef.getColList("", "E.[COL_NAME]", ",
			", "", "PK")%> having count(*) > 1 ) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_SESS_NO, ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getAK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getAK("KEY_NAME")%>', 'AK', <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CT_NAME","A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E where <%=odiRef.getAKColList("", "("+odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) 
		or	 (("+odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is null) 
		and (E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "
		and	", "")%> group by <%=odiRef.getAKColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
			", "")%> having count(*) > 1 ) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_SESS_NO, ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getFK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getFK("FK_NAME")%>', 'FK', <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> <%if (odiRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL").equals("")) {%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")%> where not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> PK where <%=odiRef.getFKColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME]	= PK.[PK_COL_NAME]", "
		and	", "")%> ) and <%=odiRef.getFKColList("", odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_ALIAS")+".[COL_NAME] is not null", "
		and	", "")%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>
<%} else {%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getFK("FK_ALIAS")%> where not exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "FK_PK_TABLE_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getFK("PK_ALIAS")%> where <%=odiRef.getFK("COMPLEX_SQL")%> ) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%}%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_SESS_NO, ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getCK("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getCK("COND_NAME")%>', 'CK', <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> <%=odiRef.getCK("COND_ALIAS")%> where not ( <%=odiRef.getCK("COND_SQL")%> ) <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> ( ODI_SESS_NO, ODI_ERR_TYPE, ODI_ERR_MESS, ODI_ORIGIN, ODI_CHECK_DATE, ODI_CONS_NAME, ODI_CONS_TYPE, <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> ) select '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>', '<%=odiRef.getNotNullCol("MESS")%>', '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>', <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_DATE_FCT")%>, '<%=odiRef.getSqlQuotedString(odiRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME"))%>', 'NN', <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "MAP and !UD1")%> from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> where <%=odiRef.getNotNullCol("COL_NAME")%> is null <%=odiRef.getFilter()%>

delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")%> where exists ( select 'X' from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> <%=odiRef.getInfo("DEST_TAB_ALIAS_WORD")%> E <%if (odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE").equals("F")) {%> where <%=odiRef.getColList("","(("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) or ("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null and E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\t\tand\t", "", "UK")%> <%}else{%> where <%=odiRef.getColList("","(("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] = E.[COL_NAME]) or ("+odiRef.getTable("L", "CT_NAME", "A")+".[COL_NAME] is null and E.[COL_NAME] is null))", "\n\t\tand\t", "", "PK")%> <%}%> and ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' and ODI_SESS_NO = '<%=odiRef.getSession("SESS_GUID")%>' )
insert check sum into check table

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","CHECK_NAME", "W")%> ( CATALOG_NAME, SCHEMA_NAME, RESOURCE_NAME, FULL_RES_NAME, ERR_TYPE, ERR_MESS, CHECK_DATE, ORIGIN, CONS_NAME, CONS_TYPE, ERR_COUNT ) select '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("CATALOG")%>', '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("SCHEMA")%>', '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_NAME")%>', <% if (odiRef.getTargetTable("TECHNO_NAME").matches("XML")) { out.print("'" + odiRef.getInfo("DEST_SCHEMA") + "' || '." + odiRef.getTargetTable("RES_NAME") + "'"); } else out.print("'" + odiRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","D") + "'"); %>, E.ODI_ERR_TYPE, E.ODI_ERR_MESS, E.ODI_CHECK_DATE, E.ODI_ORIGIN, E.ODI_CONS_NAME, E.ODI_CONS_TYPE, count(*) from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","ERR_NAME", "W")%> E where E.ODI_ERR_TYPE = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ERR_TYPE")%>' and E.ODI_ORIGIN = '<%=odiRef.getInfo("CT_ORIGIN")%>' group by E.ODI_ERR_TYPE, E.ODI_ERR_MESS, E.ODI_CHECK_DATE, E.ODI_ORIGIN, E.ODI_CONS_NAME, E.ODI_CONS_TYPE
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.create check table
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.drop error table
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.create error table
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert PK errors
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert AK errors
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert FK errors
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert CK errors
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert Not Null errors
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.delete errors from controlled table
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.insert check sum into check table
CKM MSSQL Azure PDW.drop check table
